room_title: Escape room "Dr. K’s Lethal Injection" by Escape MKE in Milwaukee
review: We did Dr. K's Lethal Injection and LOVED IT!! It was challenging for 4 people and we were so so so close to escaping. Worth every penny. Great staff and awesome technology.
